<p>The first part of the session (recording below) is a recorded presentation and the second part (unrecorded) was a group discussion to learn from one another on how others have engaged in similar partnerships and courses, including challenges and ways to overcome them. </p>
	<h2>Learning Sessions</h2>
     <h3><strong>Ready: </strong>Introduction</h3>
<p>Anisa Saleh  introduces the MCH CELL series, links the content of MCH CELL to the MCH Leadership Competencies, and introduces the speakers for the session.</p>
